look

public List<AuxFunctions.LookUpResult> look(ChemicalPattern<?>[] patterns,
                                            ListTerm<?> x)

Lookup Function.

Checks if the provided (variable) ListTerm is assigned to some property in some filter in one of the provided patterns.

Parameters:
patterns - A list of patterns on which execute the lookup
x - The ?x variable to be searched
Returns:
A list of results, reporting PatternName, PropertyTerm and the ?x variable itself
